.setSecurityManager(...)` requires that startup flag.\n- Propagates current `-javaagent` arguments to the forked JVM so JaCoCo line coverage can be recorded for the fallback path.\n\nNo metadata or native-image configuration files were modified.\n\nI did not compile or run tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05c25c4fd7dbb290016a27626ff56881949bd8c361445c529d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1473, "output": 939, "cacheRead": 50688, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 53100, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1780965979509, "responseId": "resp_05c25c4fd7dbb290016a27625c2e788194a5d0a48b1a452caf"}, "toolResults": []}
